social_posts.post_text: Happy Birthday to the best big sister anyone could ever ask for! You’re always there for me whether I need a good laugh, a shoulder to cry on, a Diet Coke from McDonalds cause it’s “the best kind”, or just a day with you by my side. Thank you for being you, and thank you to my Mother for birthing mine and Joey’s bff. I love you 🤍 @kelliisking

What’s more awkward, people singing happy birthday to you or trying to take a cute photo with mom and not knowing how to pose? 🤷🏼‍♀️ Happy Birthday Mama! Love you 🫶🏼 @3xkingmom
A magical birthday for the most magical friend✨ thank you for being you @dniederhoffer I’d be lost without ya

Happy Birthday to my soul friend🫶🏼 The friend that for over a decade has felt like family. The friend that makes me cry from laughter, and always reminds me of my power. I love you my TT! I can’t wait to celebrate you✨ @titinaserena
I think @titinaserena birthday wish must have been for me to not get seasick cause we were smoooooth sailing🌊
Not sure what I expected but this was not it 🤢
Burrata, booze, and boobs @joeyking

Last night was magical✨ thank you @joeyking for letting me be a part of this special night…I couldn’t be more proud of you!! Over 3.5 hours of pure joy aka  @taylorswift . Haven’t stopped smiling since💖 Best. Night. Ever.
In our Lover and 1989 Eras✨💖💙 Best night with the best people @joeyking @aerie #aeriereal #aeriepartner
The best weekend with the best people, and the best wine. Napa was the perfect place for @joeyking bachelorette party! 🤍💍☁️ #thebrideisoncloud9

Happy Birthday to my best friend and the source of 99% of my laughter. To the one who makes ordinary moments magical and lights up every room she walks into. And to the one who has pantsed me more times than I can count. I love you bud🤍 @joeyking

My lil sis is married 🥹 For the l ast couple of days I’ve been trying to think of a way to put last weekend into words.. and to be honest nothing I write out quite encapsulates what a beautiful, magical wedding it was. We danced (till almost 3am), we cried happy tears (ok I cried a lottt of happy tears), and we didn’t stop smiling once. I couldn’t be happier that these two found each other and now get to spend forever together🤍 truly the most incredible wedding for the most incredible people💍🥂 @joeyking @stevenpiet
Life Lately 🍂🎈🫶🏼🐾🎃🌾✨

Our movie Give Me Your Eyes is premiering on Amazon LatAm November 15th! This was such a fun one to work on and I met some of the most incredible people while filming this! US release dates coming soon!

Happy birthday to the most amazing lady who I am lucky enough to call my grandma❤️ Anyone who knows her knows that she has the kindest soul and a heart that is filled with so much love and compassion for others. I love you to infinity Grandma, and I hope your day is as beautiful as you are ❤️ @redsfarrar

A couple of days late but wanted to thank 2023 for all the lessons it taught me. One of those was reminding me to always keep going even when it feels like you can’t, because truthfully you never know what life has waiting around the corner. These are a few of those “around the corner” moments 2023 brought me❤️
